    <sampling_method>Non-Probability Sample</sampling_method>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  informed consent to participate in the study signed by the patient / relative of the
             patient / the legal representative of the patient

          -  age over 18 years

          -  stroke, confirmed by neuroimaging

          -  light to moderate stroke (score on National Institutes of Health Stroke Scale).

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  recanalization therapy

          -  previous epileptic seizures and history of epilepsy

          -  psychiatric diseases in history

          -  previous stroke

          -  traumatic brain injury

          -  brain tumors.

          -  inflammatory and infectious diseases

          -  decompensated physical illness.

          -  pregnancy.
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
